<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/mycokeys.100.112458.figure6>
    dc:description "Figure 6. Tulostoma shaihuludii: a FP- 2020 - 12 - 01 - 3, Fueloephaza b, d-g FP- 2016 - 12 - 11 (BP 112643, holotype), Tazlar c AL- 2021 - 01 - 24, Bocsa h FP- 2017 - 12 - 09, Orgovany a-c basidiocarps d, e basidiospores f, g capillitium with basidiospores h thin-walled, septate capillitium hyphae. Scale bars: 1 µm (d); 10 µm (e); 20 µm (f-h). Photos: a, b, e-h P. Finy c L. Albert d K. Boka." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/944694" ;
